name: The Asunta Case
overview: After two parents report that their 12-year-old daughter Asunta is missing, the investigation soon turns against them.

episodes.name: September 21
episodes.overview: Rosario and Alfonso report their adopted daughter, Asunta, as missing. But what police assume is a kidnapping quickly spirals into something sinister.

episodes.name: September 24
episodes.overview: The investigation discloses unexpected details about Rosario's love life. A new testimony goes over Asunta's last months and points to alarming signs.

episodes.name: September 26
episodes.overview: As questions and evidence mount, public opinion turns against Rosario and Alfonso, whose relationship proves to be more turbulent than it looked.

episodes.name: September 28
episodes.overview: The defense attorney switches gears and reveals that Asunta had been targeted in the past. However, the new evidence seems off to Judge Malvar.

episodes.name: 24 Hours
